OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1778746040
OL,3,CTwo arrested after tractor crashed
OL,4,Cinto house with people evacuated from
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FTwo men have been arrested after a
OL,8,Ftractor crashed into a house in
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough, with nearby residents
OL,10,Fevacuated from their homes.
OL,12,FCleveland Police were called after
OL,13,Freports a motor vehicle crashed into a
OL,14,Fproperty in Priory Road at around 1am
OL,15,Fon Saturday 9 May.
OL,17,FResidents from two households, who
OL,18,Fwere evacuated from their homes, are
OL,19,Fstill unable to return as a precaution.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
