PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1778746040
OL,3,CTwo arrested after tractor crashed
OL,4,Cinto house with people evacuated from
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FTwo men, aged 27 and 34, have been
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of conspiracy to
OL,9,Fdestroy or damage property and theft
OL,10,Fof a motor vehicle.
OL,12,FThey are currently in police custody
OL,13,Ffor questioning.
OL,15,FThe force has said officers will
OL,16,Fremain working with the local
OL,17,Fauthority to arrange for structural
OL,18,Fengineers to assess the property and
OL,19,Fensure it is made safe.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
