PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1778746040
OL,3,CTwo arrested after tractor crashed
OL,4,Cinto house with people evacuated from
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FIt has said it's likely the scene will
OL,8,Fneed to remain in place for the next
OL,9,Ffew days.
OL,11,FSpecialist forensic teams are set to
OL,12,Fcarry out detailed examinations,
OL,13,Fincluding the tractor involved which
OL,14,Fis believed to be stolen from Yarm.
OL,16,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,17,FDetective Chief Inspector, John Bonner
OL,18,Fsaid: "Our investigation is moving at
OL,19,Fpace with various enquiries taking
OL,20,Fplace that has led to two arrests.
OL,26,@zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
