CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1778746040
OL,3,CTwo arrested after tractor crashed
OL,4,Cinto house with people evacuated from
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,F"I am aware of video footage
OL,8,Fcirculating on social media which
OL,9,Fappears to show activity at farm
OL,10,Flocations across Cleveland, North
OL,11,FYorkshire, and Durham prior to the
OL,12,Fincident and would ask for the owners
OL,13,Fto report this to us.
OL,15,F"I'm taking this opportunity to appeal
OL,16,Fdirectly to farm and landowners to
OL,17,Fcontact us if they have any CCTV or
OL,18,Finformation relating to intruders or
OL,19,Fsuspicious activity on their land
OL,20,Fwithin the last seven days.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
