OL,3,CTwo arrested after tractor crashed
OL,4,Cinto house with people evacuated from
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,F"There will continue to be an
OL,8,Fincreased police presence in the area
OL,9,Fto provide reassurance to the
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,FAnyone with information, dashcam or
OL,13,Fdoorbell footage ` including sightings
OL,14,Fof the vehicle ` can contact Cleveland
OL,15,FPolice on 101 or visit the website
OL,16,Fquoting reference number 087639.
OL,18,FInformation can be provided
OL,19,Fanonymously by calling Crimestoppers
OL,20,Fon 0800 555 111.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]
